I like the ones with well-defined features Min Ji.

00:38:08.119 --> 00:38:10.489
That's my type.

00:38:15.500 --> 00:38:16.530
Okay.

00:38:17.000 --> 00:38:18.730
I'll accept your apology because I'm awesome.

