Be nice to Se Kyung when I'm gone.

00:41:03.170 --> 00:41:04.769
Don't treat him like a servant.

00:41:05.130 --> 00:41:06.739
Be sincerely nice to him...

00:41:07.599 --> 00:41:08.670
as his friend.

