Yes. Sure.

00:41:41.239 --> 00:41:42.610
One couple's combo, please.

00:41:44.739 --> 00:41:45.769
Please enjoy.

00:41:56.820 --> 00:41:58.289
If we're having a couple's combo,

00:41:59.389 --> 00:42:00.590
does it make us a couple?

