Shouldn't you spend the last day with Se Kyung?

00:43:15.059 --> 00:43:17.099
He must be waiting for you to tell him the truth.

00:43:19.699 --> 00:43:20.769
It'll be better...

00:43:22.769 --> 00:43:23.769
if he doesn't know.

